<event name="SYLVAN_SALT_QUEST_INTRO_CHAOS">
	<text>You step aboard the lodge, feeling almost as if you're meant to expect someone here. Yet, no one steps forward. You wander around until you catch an intriguing conversation between a Clansman and a pirate concerning an individual called the "Saltman". You sit down at the table adjacent to them and lean in closer to hear what they're saying.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Listen.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Suddenly, you hear a loud and obnoxious voice ringing in your ear, that causes you to fall out of your chair. You look up and see the gnome has mysteriously appeared on the table and is now yelling at you. Annoyed at your strange behavior, the station owners ask you to leave. You apologize and blame it on the gnome, which only confuses them more. After some arguing back and forth whether the gnome is real or not, you head back to the ship and find a mysterious set of coordinates pinned to your dashboard with a note. "Please find him for me. -S"</text>
			<playSound>gm_obyn</playSound>
			<quest event="NEBULA_SALT_QUEST_CHAOS"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="SYLVAN_SALT_QUEST_INTRO">
	<text>You start to move around the lodge, when you notice a familiar face in the back of the crowd. "Sssstranger! Well what are the oddsss! What are the oddssss indeed... Looking for ssssomething to buy? I can take you 'round to my ssship and ssshow you what I've got..."</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Follow Sylvan.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You follow Sylvan out back, where he makes small talk on the way. "You know, I wasss onccce a Ranger amongssst the Guild. Then we got over thisss dissspute with this fellow called the Sssalt Man. Lasssst of hisss kind, and a fearsssome bounty hunter to boot. But the Guild wantsss him dead, a terrible ssshame. Jusssst couldn't bring mysssself to it, you know? Anywayssss, about that ssstuff..."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Tell me more about the Salt Man.</text>
				<event>
					<text>Sylvan looks down at the ground for a moment. "Heh, piqued your interessst, have I? A fassscinating fellow he wasss, and perhapsss the only reason I left the clan and became a merchant insssstead. You could cccertainly call usss... friendsss... but I haven't spoken with him in yearsss..."</text>
					<choice>
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event>
							<text>"Truth be told ssstranger, I came here to find him again... hmmm... think you could do me a favor ssstranger, and ssstop by these coordinatesss would you? I've heard thatss where he'sss holding out currently. Onccce you're there, make sssure he ain't dead, alright? And put in a good word for me... I would really appreccciate it ssstranger."</text>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Accept.</text>
								<event load="SYLVAN_SALT_QUEST_ACCEPT"/>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Why don't you do it yourself?</text>
								<event>
									<text>"Ah... well, I'm a very busssy Sssslug ssstranger. You know how it issss, travelling the realitiessss vassst and all that jazz. It'sss jussst a little check in anywaysss, you know? It'ssss not like he'sss in any danger. I jussst want to make sure he'sss okay. And he'sss going to be okay. Of courssse. Heheh..." Sylvan doesn't sound too sure of himself but says nothing more.</text>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Accept.</text>
										<event load="SYLVAN_SALT_QUEST_ACCEPT"/>
									</choice>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Decline.</text>
										<event load="SYLVAN_SALT_QUEST_DECLINE"/>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
							<!--<choice hidden="true" req="unique_obyn">
								<text>(Obyn) *Cough*</text>
								<event>
									<text>"Oh... Obyn! You're- you're here? Oh... uhm. Well, not my Obyn."</text>
									
								</event>
							</choice>-->
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Decline.</text>
								<event load="SYLVAN_SALT_QUEST_DECLINE"/>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>See what he's got.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Aaaah ssstranger, you're in luck. I've got my handssss on sssome high quality gear I have a feeling you'll be interesssted in!" Sylvan pulls some weapons out of his ship and shows them to you.</text>
					<choice>
						<text>Agree.</text>
						<event load="SYLVAN_TRADES"/>
					</choice>
					<choice>
						<text>Decline.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"Aaaah, oh well then Sssstranger. For another time then, perhapsss? I have faith we'll ssssee each other again down the line!"</text>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="SYLVAN_SALT_QUEST_ACCEPT">
	<text>"Ah! Now that'ssss grand, ssstranger! You Renegadesss, ssso reliable. That'sss why I like you, ssstranger. Now, how do you feel about a little trade?"</text>
	<quest event="NEBULA_SALT_QUEST"/>
	<choice>
