			<text>You approach the asteroid, marveling at the sheer size of it. It's almost as large as your ship! That's when you come to a realization - it IS a ship! It remains motionless as you approach, and you suspect it might be empty.</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_SALT_ABANDONED" hostile="false"/>
