					<text>It seems much like your previous asteroid theory, the empty ship theory is also untrue. A skeleton crew of various races rises to meet you. "Crap, looks like one of the Guild's bounty hunters found us while the boss is out! Rally up men, we'll put these mercs in their place!" You can probably get out of this without killing them, but you doubt they'll be willing to talk until you rough up their hull a bit.</text>
