	<text>"We were running a mission to take out one of the Guild's less... hospitable dissection centers, when the boss ran into some trouble. He got captured and is held there currently, but we escaped. His last orders were for us to stay here in the ship and hide. We're in no condition for a jailbreak, especially not after this little brawl, but you might just be the Renegade for the job, especially with Sylvan on your side!"</text>
