<event name="NEBULA_SALT_QUEST_2">
	<beaconType id="map_icon_merchantquest_major" global="true">
        <color r="155" g="90" b="205" a="1.0"/>
        <unvisitedTooltip>This is the location of a quest.</unvisitedTooltip>
        <visitedTooltip>Explored location. Nothing left of interest.</visitedTooltip>
    </beaconType>
	<quest>
		<nebulaBeacon>true</nebulaBeacon>
		<createNebula>false</createNebula>
		<aggressive>2</aggressive>
	</quest>
	<preventFleet/>
	<text>You find yourself in yet another clearing, and see a massive bay. It's very pleasant looking and you aren't sure where the Clansmen could possibly be keeping something as sinister as a "dissection center"... until you look towards the sky.</text>
	<img back="BACK_EVENT_CLANJAIL" planet="NONE"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Wow, that's big.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Indeed, the facility is so massive it blocks out nearly all of the perceivable sky, yet the market down below bustles with life as if there wasn't just a massive foreboding facility floating above them.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Just fly up to the facility, what could go wrong?</text>
				<event>
					<text>Turns out, many things. As soon as you pass by the barrier to the dissection center's hangar, a massive Anti-ship cannon on the interior swivels to face your ship, and several Clansmen start shouting at you. "The hell you doin' you git? You got a licccensssse to be in here?"</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Of course!</text>
						<event>
							<text>The Clansman takes a moment to look you dead in the eye. "Then how goesss the motto of the guild?"</text>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Rule thy mind, rule they honor!</text>
								<event load="SALT_QUEST_2_MOTTO_WRONG"/>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>A valiant death before a cowardly life!</text>
								<event load="SALT_QUEST_2_MOTTO_WRONG"/>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Who is better is greater than the rest!</text>
								<event load="SALT_QUEST_2_MOTTO_WRONG"/>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>I think YOU just forgot, and you're asking me so that you don't look stupid.</text>
								<event>
									<text>"What? The hell are you-" The Clansman is cut off by one of his friends. "He's right Percccy, DO you know the guild motto?" The Clansman stutters. "W-well... I uh- Well I bet you don't know it either!" The other Clansman brings his tentacle up to the back of his head and scratches nervously. "Yeah... I guessss you're right. Does anyone here know?" All of the other Clansmen in the room look at each other and shake their heads.</text>
									<choice hidden="true">
