<event name="SALT_QUEST_2_SUCCESS_CHAOS">
	<text>You've finally made your way to the prison hold, labeled "Exotic Creature Containment." You shoot a couple guards on the way, picking up a keycard from one of them, which you use to unlock the Salt Man's cell, where you find a massive gray creature leaning against a wall as if waiting for you. "I'm going to take a shot in the dark and say you aren't with the Guild, considering that green ooze all over your chest seems like it belongs to someone else." He sticks out his massive hand. "Name's Obyn, though most just call me 'Salt Man'. Take the view in while you can, I'm not a sight you see often."</text>
