		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_CLAN">
		<text>(Guild Crew) Offer them a list of destinations.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Oh, you're one of them! I greatly appreciate your offer, but there's no need. We already bought a map earlier, we can give you a copy if you'd like!"</text>
			<reveal_map/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="weapons" lvl="5">
		<text>(Upg. Weapons) Give me everything you have or die.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"By the crypt! No need to be so hostile! We'll give you anything you want!" The Crystals send over some supplies.</text>
			<autoReward level="LOW">stuff</autoReward>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="MORALITY_UPDATE_CRYSTAL"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL">
		<text>(Crystal Crew) Request supplies.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Oh, hello friend! I assume there's some lovely souvenir you're dying to buy, but are short on cash, and I'm happy to help!" The Crystals send over some scrap, and you don't bother mentioning you're a military vessel.</text>
			<autoReward level="MED">scrap_only</autoReward>
