	<ship load="SHIP_CLAN_CRISIS" hostile="false"/>
	<status type="limit" target="enemy" system="teleporter" amount="0"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Hail them.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The ship responds and shows a Clansman frantically clawing at his feelers. "How did I get here? Why isss thisss what my life hasss become? A ssshadow of a perssson, a violent killer..."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Put this man out of his misery.</text>
				<event>
					<text>You arm your weapons and attack the Clansman. It looks as though they aren't even trying to fight back.</text>
					<status type="limit" target="enemy" system="weapons" amount="0"/>
					<status type="limit" target="enemy" system="drones" amount="0"/>
					<status type="limit" target="enemy" system="hacking" amount="0"/>
					<status type="limit" target="enemy" system="mind" amount="0"/>
