				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="NEBULA_CLAN_TAX" unique="true">
	<text>You've only just barely entered the beacon when a Clansman ship flies past, tailed by several large Clairvoyant vessels. You know the EHG is still a part of the Kleptocracy, so you can't imagine why they might be sending the enforcers out here.</text>
	<environment type="nebula"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Chase them.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You pursue the Slugs through the nebula, where you find the Clansmen have hunkered up in a cave, and won't come out. The Clairvoyants appear to be at a loss.</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_CLAIRVOYANT_TAX" hostile="false"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Ask them about the situation.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"You ssssee, normally the Kleptocracccy doessssn't get involved in EHG affairsss, but their membersss are ssstill cccitizensss of our nation, and they have taxesss to pay. Assss you can tell, the men who've locked themssselvesss in that cave owe... quite a lot."</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>How much?</text>
						<event>
							<text>"Ohhh, uh, about 17 million. In Kleptocracy Oseroes. If I wasss to transsslate that into ssscrap, which ssseems to be the currencccy around here, it comesss to around... 260 million."</text>
							<choice>
								<text>Use some missiles to blow the Clansmen out of the cave.</text>
								<event>
									<text>You lay the bombs all around the cave then wait for them to explode. The impact sends the cave crumbling in and forcing the Clansmen out, where they're arrested.</text>
									<item_modify>
										<item type="missiles" min="-7" max="-7"/>
									</item_modify>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Continue...</text>
										<event load="NEBULA_CLAN_TAX_SAVEKLEPT"/>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Fight the Clairvoyants to aid the Clansmen.</text>
								<event>
									<text>You're known to be one to commit many crimes yourself in your travels. Though yours are normally warcrimes and this is a case of tax evasion, that doesn't mean you can't help a fellow criminal out. In the name of the Federation, of course.</text>
									<ship hostile="true"/>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Continue...</text>
										<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_SLUG">
								<text>(Slug Crew) Try to reason with the Clansmen.</text>
								<event>
									<text>Your Slug goes up to the awning of the cave, where he speaks with the Clansmen. Playing off of their better reason, he convinces them that dying trapped in a cave is a far worse fate than going to prison, even if it's a Slug one. This works, and the Clansmen surrender.</text>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Continue...</text>
										<event load="NEBULA_CLAN_TAX_SAVEKLEPT"/>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_SLUG_KING">
								<text>(Ex-Slug King) "Perhapsss I can pardon them?"</text>
								<event>
									<text>"Oh! Uh, sssir! I didn't sssee you there, my king. Er, ex-king. I don't... you don't really have authority over thisss sssir, but I'm a Clairvoyant, and I think you did great thingsss for our nation, even if you weren't the bessst leader at timesss. If you're willing to ssstand up for thessse men though, I won't quessstion it." The Slug clears their debts, then flies away.</text>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Continue...</text>
										<event load="NEBULA_CLAN_TAX_SAVECLAN"/>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>No reason getting involved further.</text>
								<event/>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>What a funky and unpredictable situation. Anyways, I'm bored; time to move on.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You now have some time on your hands.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="NEBULA_CLAN_TAX_SAVECLAN">
	<text>You approach the Clansmen, who whisper "Are they gone?" Once you assure them the Clairvoyants are gone, they exit the cave and thank you. "Haha! Tax evasssion worksss out flawlesssly onccce again. Uh... I guessss I ssshould reward you. How about a reactor upgrade?"</text>
	<upgrade amount="1" system="reactor"/>
</event>
<event name="NEBULA_CLAN_TAX_SAVEKLEPT">
	<text>"Ah, well that handlessss that. Thank you, Federation. Didn't know you had interessst in helping with Kleptocracccy affairsss. Perhapsss a bit of scrap will help compenssate for your help in ressolving thisss isssue."</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">scrap_only</autoReward>
</event>

