<event name="NEBULA_DISTRESS_CLAN_GHOST" unique="true">
	<text>You aren't sure from where, but you're receiving a hail from a Guild Ranger. "Up for a bit of work? Ssssome Ghossstsss sssstole my ssship! I intend to get it back, through any methodsss I can, and you look like a damn well efficcccient one."</text>
	<environment type="nebula"/>
	<distressBeacon/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Accept.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Good, good! Jusssst pleassse don't dessstroy it!"</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_CLAN_GHOST" hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice> 
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Decline.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You aren't some chump change mercenary. You have standards! You mute the Slug.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
