<event name="KNIGHT_PALACE_RESOLUTION_SLOCKNOG_REAL">
	<text>Once Nights' corpse has been recovered, he is moved to a hearse ship for later. The crown too is recovered, broken but miraculously not obliterated. The Slugs gather together to discuss what to do next.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
