						<text>These people need further influence - use a show of force to put Slocknog back in power.</text>
						<event>
							<text>Considering you've become so heavily involved in Slug politics already, you might as well go the extra mile. You head back to your ship and approach, firing a warning shot upon the crowd. Once you have everyone's attention, you demand Slocknog be in charge once again. The crowd is reluctant, but the Clairvoyants remain loyal to their king and move to support him.</text>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Continue...</text>
