							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Suggest that the Slugs hold an election the proper way - through a vote.</text>
						<event>
							<text>Surprisingly, this revolutionary idea is not immediately rejected. Persuaded by recent events, the Slugs seem to genuinely consider settling their differences and staging a government reform for the better good. However, one member of the crowd inquires, "Then what ssshall happen to Sssslocknog?"</text>
							<variable name="loc_slugdemocracy" op="set" val="1"/>
							<choice hidden="true">
