									<text>"I- what? You have ssspent ssso much effort to help me, and yet now you ssssentence me to death?" Slocknog attempts to run, but is quickly caught by some other Slugs and dragged away. You are thanked and rewarded by the Slugs citizens who you have helped so greatly.</text>
