<event name="KNIGHT_PALACE_RESOLUTION_NIGHTS">
	<text>As Slocknog's cruiser crashes into the lake, the fighting suddenly seems to come to a halt. You land your ship next to the Black Raven, where Nights is chuckling. "HAH! That'll ssshow that idiot what happenssss when you messs with Nights baby!" Nights pumps his tentacle into the air triumphantly, and you don't bother mentioning you did all of the work.</text>
