		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>You watch as the Slugs get together a team to fish the cruiser out of the lake. Once Slocknog's corpse has been recovered, he is moved to a hearse ship for later. The Slugs gather around, trying to decide how to proceed with the festival.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
