					<text>Furious, Nights storms up to them demanding they hand back to the crown to him, but the crowd refuses. "You basssstard, you don't dessserve ssshit! Had you jussst done your duty asss a king and handled thisss asss ssomething other than an overgrown man-child, we wouldn't have the corpsssess of dozensss sssmoldering in front of the Royal palaccce!" Shouts someone from the crowd, shockingly appearing to be straight from Nights' inner circle.</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event>
							<text>These words seem to resonate with nearly everyone present, and soon a mob has formed, marching towards Nights, demanding he be punished. The only reason no one suggests executing him is because no one has any clue who to elect in his stead.</text>
