		<event>
			<text>"Ah, didn't think there wasss anyone elsse here who wassssn't busssy getting their asss handed to them by Nightsss'ss men. Idiotsss don't even know the Palaccce isssn't in a nebula, and that there'ssss no way Nightsss would dare leave the comfort of his hidey-hole."</text>
