<event name="NEBULA_KNIGHT_QUIZ" unique="true"> <!--basically free stuff with extra flavor unless you're stupid-->
	<text>It's not too common to see Clairvoyant ships about, but you've seen far less than expected here in this Slug-filled nebula. It seems you've finally run into one though, and they aren't firing on you just yet. Instead, it looks like they want to communicate.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_SLUG_ELITE_FIGHT" hostile="false"/> 
	<environment type="nebula"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Respond.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"If our data issss correct, might it be true that you are the ssship everyone iss talking about? The one that hasss brought back to usss Ssslocknog, our great king?"</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Yes.</text>
				<event>
