			<text>The smuggler captain appears on the screen. Though he tries to put on a menacing appearance, you can tell from his eager smug grin he's pleased by the prospect of another client. "If you're looking for guns or explosives, can't help you there Feddy boy. I'm on an express trip to Nights himself to deliver some brain melting power. These narcotics sell for premium price among the Slugs here, though not much in any other place."</text>
