<event name="NEBULA_KNIGHT_DUEL" unique="true">
	<text>Out of nowhere, a Slug beams aboard your ship, brandishing a long sword. "On guard ye! I challenge you to a duel. Non-fatal, of coursssse. Defeat me and I will give you all the sssscrap my sssship carriessss. Lossse, and I take all of your fuel. Decline, and I shall leave without another word."</text>
