<textList name="NEBULA_KNIGHT_CLAIRVOYANT_FIGHT">
	<text>The Clairvoyants are primarily in favor of Slocknog, but despite this it seems the ship here has chosen protecting their homeland over letting a foreign Federation ship rumored to be supporting their king running about.</text>
	<text>Though you haven't encountered as many Clairvoyant ships as you might have expected in a dense Slug nebula like this, it appears your luck has run out.</text>
	<text>A Clairvoyant ship has chosen to do their job and protect their sector, and is moving in to attack.</text>
	<text>"Federation, you aren't ssssuppossssed to be here! Thissss isss a private sssector!" A Clairvoyant ship moves in to attack.</text>
</textList>

